# Resume Engine

- Document pipeline: resolve → validate → format → export (PDF, DOCX, LaTeX, cover letter).
- Respect page budget and fit-band rules in `format-rules.ts` and `fit-bands.ts` — do not bypass validation.
- Platform-specific formatting lives in `platform-format.ts`; keep ATS-safe output.
- Types and schemas: `src/shared/resume-engine/types.ts` and `src/shared/resume-types.ts`.
